      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop <strong>half</strong> your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>shallot </strong>finely</p><p>Peel and roughly chop your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and slice finely</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1658227982253-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1658227982253-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1658227982253-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1658227982253-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1658227982253-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>beef mince</strong> to a large bowl with the <strong>chopped shallot</strong></p><p>Add <strong>half </strong>your<strong> ground smoked paprika </strong>with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and mix thoroughly until fully combined – this is your<strong> cevapi mixture</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1658227989591-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1658227989591-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1658227989591-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1658227989591-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1658227989591-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the<strong> cevapi mixture</strong> and roll into 3 little sausage shapes per person – these are your <strong>patties</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>patties </strong>to a baking tray (or two!) with a little drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven[s] for 12-15 min or until cooked through and browned (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>cevapi</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1658227994373-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1658227994373-x400.jpg",
