          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1658227997516-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> soft cheese</strong> to a medium bowl with your<strong> feta</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and the <strong>remaining white wine vinegar </strong>and give everything a good mix up until smooth – this is your <strong>kaymak cheese</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred finely</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1658228001149-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1658228001149-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1658228001149-x700.jpg",
