            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half and place in the toaster for 1-2 min or until lightly toasted</p><p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong> with your <strong>remaining smoked paprika</strong> – this is your <strong>smoky mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-1718716509009-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-1718716509009-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-1718716509009-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-1718716509009-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-1718716509009-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fill the <strong>toasted ciabatta </strong>with the <strong>smoky mayo</strong>, <strong>some</strong> of the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, the <strong>cevapi</strong> and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>kaymak cheese</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> sliced shallot </strong>and drizzle over <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chilli dressing</strong> – this is your<strong> Serbian-style cevapi sandwich</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>chips </strong>and <strong>remaining lettuce </strong>to the side with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>kaymak cheese </strong>and the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chilli dressing</strong> all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
